      "markdown": "## 第九课口语部分Part2模拟三\n\n轻松搞定KET口语25分\n\n内容提要\n\nKET口语part2重点句型大演练KET口语part2高频必会词汇KET口语part2真题训练\n\n## KET口语 part 2 重点句型\n\n## 问时间\n\nopen/weekends?open/every day  Is it open on weekends/ every day?opening times?\n\n When does it open? / When is it open?\n\n时间的回答\n\nYes, it's open on weekends / every day / on Monday It's open from Monday to Sunday, from 9am to 8pm.It opens from Monday to Sunday, from 9am to 8pm.No, it's not open on.…, it's open from.... to …\n\n问名字\n\n问时间、地址\n\n问具体内容\n\n问附加服务信息\n\n问名字\n\nWhat's the name of.\n\nmusic shop, cafe, cinema, bookshop, club, disco \n\n回答\n\n It's called...\n\n\n\n## KET 口语 part 2 重点句型\n\n问地点\n\nWhere is …\n\n What's the address of …\n\n回答\n\nIt's in... street.\n\nThe address is .\n\n\n\n学而思网校学习有意xueersi.com ",
